---

<BaseLayout
  title="P.R.O.M.P.T Framework: The Last Prompt Engineering Guide You'll Ever Read"
  description="The P.R.O.M.P.T framework - Purpose, Results, Obstacles, Mindset, Preferences, Technical. A systematic methodology for effective AI interactions grounded in established theories."
